h4. Actor:
Administrator, Remittance User.

h4. Description:
Name of the use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [ARMS|guide:_ShowARMSPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Disbursement sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click *Manage* link.
* [Show Landing Page for "Manage Task"|guide:_ShowManageTask].
* Enter Valid input.
* Click "Search" button.
* [Show Landing Page of "Task" Details|guide:_ShowTasksDetails].
* Click "Cancel" button.
* Give the "Cancel" note in textarea.
* Click on "Cancel" button.
* Cancel "Task".

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Cancel rms task" privilege.
* Cancel note must be given.

h4. Process:
* Cancel Search "Task".


h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Update Current Status & Payment Status to Cancel.
** Show Success message.


* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].